title: Watch as One Man Attempts to Eat All the Free Birthday Food on His Big Day
text:
Advertisement - Continue Reading Below A genius/lunatic YouTuber named Kent Yoshimura had the idea of trying to eat and drink all the Birthday freebies on his big day, and then he did it. I've dreamt of living such a life, but I've never had the ~true passion~ it takes to commit to such an endeavor. Bravo, Kent! You deserve the $94.54-worth of freebies you consumed, and probably also the accompanying heart burn. Beauty is pain, birthday boy!
Follow Laura on Twitter .
